Adadin mutanen da suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji hukumar bada agajin bala'i a kasar a farkon ranar Lahadi.
Rahotanni sun bayyana cewa mutane da dama sun makale a cikin gine-ginen da suka rushe a lokacin girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita 6, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar, a wani taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, mai yawan mutane sama da 380,000, ya cika da tarkacen gine-ginen da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 bisa zargin kisan kai bayan da ya kashe wata mata da wuka
An fara binciken kisan kai bayan an gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside.
An gano wanda aka kashe, mai shekara 44, da raunukan bindiga a Grayson Mews da ke kan titin John da misalin karfe 7:55 na safiyar yau. An kuma kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 da ake zargi da kisan kai.
'Yan sanda sun bukaci mutanen yankin da suka ga wani abu su bayar da rahoto.
