Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli, da kuma matar da ta tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da tashoshin da ke dakatar da shirye-shiryen yau da kullun saboda juyin juya halin ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da binciken mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taɓa ta yayin da yake bugu kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin tuɓe ta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya yi, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan sauraron, kamar yadda Nielsen ta samu a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu lambobin sauran tashoshin da suka watsa shi ba, kamar PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu sauraro a ofisoshin.
Don a ba ku ɗan haske, wannan matakin kallon ne kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko na bikin Oscar.
Kafofin watsa labarai na Fox News Channel, wadanda masu sharhi suka ba da goyon baya ga nadin Kavanaugh, sun jagoranci dukkan tashoshin talabijin tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a yayin sauraron da ya gudana duk rana, Nielsen ya ruwaito.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Bayan haka CBS da miliyan 3.1 NBC da miliyan 2.94 MSNBC da miliyan 2.89 da CNN da miliyan 2.52, Nielsen ya ce.
Amma, sha'awar ta ci gaba bayan an kammala shari'ar.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin dan majalisa mai matsakaici ya fitar da wata sanarwa da ke cewa za su kada kuri'arsu ga Kavanaugh, an kama sanatan a kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar ranar Juma'a ana yi masa zagon kasa da masu zanga-zanga yayin da yake kokarin shiga lif don zuwa taron kwamitin shari'a.
Sanatan ya tsaya cak yana kallon kasa yayin da ake sukar sa kai tsaye zuwa kyamarorin CNN.
"Ina nan a gabanka", in ji wata mata.
"Kana ganin yana gaya wa kasar gaskiya ne?
An gaya mata cewa, "Kai kana da iko, amma mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa kuma ya ce kafin kofar lif ta rufe, zai sami ƙarin bayani a taron kwamitin.
Tashoshin talabijin da na rediyo duk suna watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye sa'ad da kwamitin shari'a ya kada kuri'ar da za ta ba da shawarar a ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh a majalisar dattijai.
Duk da haka, Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai a kan cewa FBI za ta bincika tuhume-tuhume da ake yi wa wanda aka zaba a mako mai zuwa, abin da 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya samu tabbaci daga abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons, sannan wasu sanatoci, ya yanke shawara.
Zaɓin Flake ya kasance mai mahimmanci, tunda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
