Ayr 38-17 Melrose: Ayr wanda ba a iya doke shi ba ya zuwa saman
Sauran wasannin biyu da aka yi a baya sun yi tasiri a kan sakamakon, amma babu shakka Ayr ya cancanci cin nasara a wannan wasa mai ban sha'awa na Tennent's Premiership.
Yanzu haka ita ce ta farko a cikin jerin, ita kaɗai ce daga cikin goma da ba ta ci nasara ba.
A ƙarshe, ƙwallon ƙafa da kuma haɗarin da suka yi ya sa 'yan wasan gida suka ci gaba, kuma kocin Peter Murchie yana da dalilin farin ciki.
"An gwada mu a wasanninmu har yanzu kuma har yanzu ba mu ci nasara ba, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki", in ji shi.
Robyn Christie na Melrose ta ce: "Ayyukan Ayr ne suka fi mana kyau wajen kula da haɗarin".
Grant Anderson ya yi kwallo a minti na 14, wanda Frazier Climo ya canza, ya sa Ayr ya ci gaba, amma katin rawaya ga kyaftin din Scotland Rory Hughes, wanda Warriors suka ba shi damar shiga wasan, ya ba Melrose damar bayyana lambobin, kuma Jason Baggot ya yi amfani da kwallo wanda ba a canza shi ba.
Climo ya kara girman Ayr ta hanyar fanareti mai yawa kafin, kafin rabin lokaci, ya zira kwallo sannan ya sake yin gwaji a kasa don sanya ci 17-5 ga Ayr a hutu.
Duk da haka, Melrose ya fara rabi na biyu sosai kuma gwajin Patrick Anderson, wanda Baggot ya canza, ya rage rashin nasara zuwa maki biyar.
An yi dogon lokaci saboda mummunan rauni daga Ruaridh Knott, wanda aka kwashe daga gado zuwa waje kuma bayan sake farawa, Ayr ya ƙarfafa jagorancin tare da gwaji na Stafford McDowall wanda Climo ya canza.
An ba da katin rawaya ga kyaftin din Ayr Blair Macpherson, kuma Melrose ya sake amfani da lambar da aka samu tare da gwajin da Bruce Colvine ya yi a ƙarshen matsin lamba.
Duk da haka, 'yan wasan gida sun dawo, kuma lokacin da aka ba Struan Hutchinson katin rawaya don ya buga Climo ba tare da kwallon ba, a cikin fanareti, MacPherson ya sanya kwallon a ƙasa a bayan maul na Ayr.
Climo ya canza, kamar yadda ya yi kusan nan da nan bayan sake farawa, bayan Kyle Rowe ya karɓi bugun David Armstrong kuma ya aika da gefen Gregor Henry zuwa gwaji na biyar na ƙungiyar gida.
Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Still Game a shirye don sabon aiki a kasuwancin abinci
Ford Kieran, tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Still Game, ya kasance a shirye ya shiga cikin masana'antar cin abinci bayan da aka sanar da cewa an nada shi darektan kamfanin cin abinci mai lasisi.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 56 ya wakilci Jack Jarvis a shahararren shirin BBC, wanda ya rubuta kuma ya shiga tare da abokin aikinsa na dogon lokaci Greg Hemphill.
Ma'auratan sun sanar da cewa kakar wasa ta tara, da za ta fara nan ba da jimawa ba, za ta zama ta ƙarshe a cikin jerin, kuma da alama Kiernan yana shirin rayuwarsa bayan Craiglang.
A cewar bayanan hukuma, shi ne darektan Adriftmorn Limited.
Actor ya ƙi yin sharhi game da labarin, kodayake wata majiya daga Scottish Sun ta ba da shawarar cewa Kiernan yana son shiga cikin "kasuwancin abinci mai kyau na Glasgow".
"Teku namu ne": Bolivia, ƙasa da ba ta da bakin teku, tana fatan kotu ta sake buɗe mata hanyar shiga tekun Pacific
Ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa suna sintiri a wani sansanin sojan ruwa da ke La Paz.
Gidajen jama'a suna ɗauke da tutar shuɗi.
Tushen jiragen ruwa daga Tafkin Titicaca zuwa Amazon suna ɗauke da taken: "Teku namu ne da gaske.
"Samun shi ne aikinmu".
A dukan ƙasar Bolivia, wadda ba ta da bakin teku, har ila akwai ƙwaƙwalwar ajiyar wani bakin teku da Chile ta rasa a cikin rikici na jini na ƙarni na 19 don albarkatu, da kuma muradin sake yin tafiya a cikin Tekun Fasifik.
Wannan fatan na iya zama mafi girma a cikin shekarun da suka gabata, yayin da Bolivia ke jiran hukuncin Kotun Duniya a ranar 1 ga Oktoba, bayan shekaru biyar na tattaunawa.
"Bolivia tana da ƙarfin hali, ruhun haɗin kai da kwanciyar hankali kuma, ba shakka, kyakkyawan hangen nesa game da sakamakon", in ji Roberto Calzadilla, jami'in diflomasiyyar Bolivia.
Yawancin 'yan Bolivian za su kalli hukuncin da kotun ta yanke a manyan allon talabijin a duk fadin kasar, suna fatan kotun Hague za ta yanke hukunci a kan korafin kasarsu, don haka bayan shekaru da dama na tattaunawa da ba ta da tabbas, Chile za ta yi sulhu, ta ba Bolivia wata hanyar fita zuwa teku.
Evo Morales, shugaban kasar Bolivia mai kwarjini, wanda ke fuskantar takaddama kan sake zabensa a shekara mai zuwa, shi ma yana da babban alhakin hukuncin da aka yanke a ranar Litinin.
"Mun kusa komawa cikin tekun Pacific", shi ne rantsuwar da shugaban ya yi a watan Agustan da ya gabata.
Amma wasu masu sharhi sun ce kotun ba za ta yanke hukunci a kan Bolivia ba, kuma ba za ta yi wani canji ba idan ta yi hakan.
Hukumar ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke Netherlands ba ta da ikon ba da yankin Chile ga wata kasa kuma ta ce ba za ta tantance sakamakon wata tattaunawa ba.
Wannan hukuncin na ICT ne kawai watanni shida bayan sauraron karshe da'awar nuna cewa da hali "ba rikitarwa", ya ce Paz Zarate, wani Chilean gwani a dokokin kasa da kasa.
Kuma ba wai kawai suna inganta batun Bolivia ba, amma shekaru huɗu da suka gabata na iya cutar da ita.
"Matsayin samun dama ga teku ya zama abin da gwamnatin Bolivia ta kwace", in ji Zárate.
Ya ce, muryoyin Morales na nuna son yin fada sun lalata wasu kyawawan halayen Chile.
A wani lokaci a nan gaba, Bolivia da Chile za su ci gaba da tattaunawa, amma zai yi matukar wuya a ci gaba da tattaunawa bayan wannan.
Kasashen biyu ba su yi musayar jakadu ba tun 1962.
Tsohon shugaban kasar Eduardo Rodríguez Veltzé, wakilin Bolivia a The Hague, ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa tsarin yanke hukunci na kotun ya yi sauri.
Ya ce, ranar Litinin mai zuwa za ta ba Bolivia "wani babban dama na shiga wani sabon zamani na dangantaka da Chile" da kuma damar "kawo karshen shekaru 139 na rashin jituwa don amfanin juna".
Calzadilla ya kuma musanta cewa Morales, wanda har yanzu yana daya daga cikin shugabannin da suka fi shahara a Latin Amurka, yana amfani da batun teku a matsayin abin hawa na siyasa.
