Lokaci da tashar YouTube na taron Trump a West Virginia
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin gangami biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake ana jiran zaben wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin Amurka, Trump na son kara samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a cikin watanni biyu masu zuwa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana yau da dare kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne da karfe 7 na yamma, agogon Gabas, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa a cikin watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai gabatar da jawabinsa a gaban kotun koli a wannan makon, wanda ya shafi Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai tsauri saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican, waɗanda ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba, su sami ci gaba.
A cewar jami'an yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump, taron gangamin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa zai "karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya baya a lokacin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga tsarin shugaban kasa wanda zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke gab da lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya yi murabus daga ambatonsa, Reuters ta ruwaito.
An shirya taron ne a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, kuma za a iya ganin cewa taron da za a yi da yamma zai jawo magoya baya "daga Ohio zuwa Pennsylvania kuma za su samu labarai daga yankin Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia karo na biyu a wannan watan, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya ragu a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don taimaka masa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna tana da karfin gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan rayuwa kafin wasan raka'a na ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi wasanni uku a jere, za a iya samun wasan tseren dare na Asabar daidai da abin da gasar Ryder ta ke bukata.
Tsuntsu mai tsalle-tsalle na motsa jiki wani ra'ayi ne na wasanni wanda aka ƙirƙira shi, amma yana da wanda 'yan wasan suka gaskata da gaske, kuma ba fiye da irin wannan gasar ba.
To, daga ina za ku ce wannan gagarumin ci gaba zai zo yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka muna kallon wannan a matsayin wani abu mai ban sha'awa, zan ce", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake barin filin wasa a ƙarshen rana.
Turai tana da ci gaba, ta ci gaba da maki hudu, kuma akwai sauran 12.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, har yanzu suna da wasu makamashi da yawa don jin daɗin, musamman idan aka yi la'akari da yadda Spieth da Justin Thomas suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga tee zuwa kore kuma yana jagoranci ta hanyar misali.
Waɗannan ihu na murna sun ƙara ƙarfi yayin da zagaye ya ci gaba, tare da mahimmin bugun da ya sanya wasan na huɗu ya zama daidai lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance ramuka biyu a baya a biyu.
Gasar da ya ci a raga ta 15 ta haifar da irin wannan ihu, irin wanda ya nuna cewa har yanzu yana gaskanta cewa tawagar Amurka tana ci gaba da gasar.
"Abin da kawai muke bukata shi ne mu mai da hankali kuma mu damu da wasanmu", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk abin da ya rage ga kowane daga cikin 'yan wasan.
Ramin 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda ba a iya jayayya da shi ba a gasar Ryder Cup.
Ƙungiyar Turai, wadda ba ta da kyau amma mai kyau, tana da hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba zai iya kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" ita ce kawai duet ba ta yin bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma kuma ta guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, a ranar Jumma'a da yamma, da kuma ranar Jumma'a da safe.
A wannan jerin, kuma saboda yadda makamashin su ke gudana daga kuma zuwa ga wannan taron masu rikici, yana tabbatar da ra'ayin cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su buga a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasa da ya fi shahara don rufe yiwuwar nasarar Turai a faɗuwar rana a Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau duka biyu a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Duk da haka, magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ta kasance da wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun doke Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon hudu a safiyar yau, a lokacin da yake tare da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu doubles a gaban tara sun jefa Spaniard da Swede cikin rami wanda basu taba kusa da fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimaka musu su fita daga cikinta.
Wasanni huɗu da kuma wasan ƙwallon ƙafa suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallon su saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin abokan tarayya, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa ko ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin wani lokaci.
Turai ta fi kowa wasa a matsayin kungiya kuma ta samu gagarumar nasara a rana ta karshe, amma wannan wasan ya nuna cewa Amurka tana da karfin gwagwarmaya wanda wasu musamman Amurkawa suka yi shakkar cewa tana da shi.
Turai ta yi gaba da 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta shiga ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da babbar nasara bayan da ta fito daga wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi nasara da Amurka da ci 10 da 6.
'Yan wasan da suka yi wahayi daga Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci nauyin da suka samu nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke fama da samun matsayi a Le Golf National, har zuwa yanzu, ta hanyar maki hudu.
Kungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, tana fafatawa don riƙe kyautar da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye wata ƙungiyar Amurka da ba ta yi nasara ba a wasan kwallon huɗu na safe, ta lashe jerin 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin wasanni biyu tare da wasanni biyu, amma ba su iya rage rashin nasara ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas a wasan da za a yi a ranar Lahadi 12 domin ta ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasa na Turai da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere lokacin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka lakafta shi da "Molliwood", bayan karshen mako mai ban sha'awa ne kawai su biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu a cikin wasanninsu hudu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin hudu, sun ƙarfafa rinjaye, sun ci Woods da ba shi da ƙarfi da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau tare da 5 & 4 mai mahimmanci.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu abubuwa masu ban mamaki, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasannin da ya buga a wasanni hudu da hudu, kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, yana hutawa yayin wasan kwallon hudu na safe, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin foursomes, ya doke 2&1 Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, na farko da na uku a cikin jerin duniya.
Amma a wannan rana mai kyau da iska mai iska a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris, Turai ba ta ci nasara ba.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar maza sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Duo ya sami nasara mai ban tsoro na 2&1 akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain, kuma daga baya ya dawo don ya doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy ta 4&3 a cikin foursomes, ya rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
