Muna da ra'ayin cewa yara ne ake amfani da su wajen yin wasan kwaikwayo ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, baƙon abu da Johnny English ya yi ba ya da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim ɗin Bean.
Yanzu, abin da ake nufi shi ne, Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin babbar hanyar leken asirin Burtaniya, ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a fagen hargitsi ga jami'in da ke aiki, wani karamin aiki ne ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shine ƙarshen farkawa ga firaminista wanda ke nuna mutum mai girman kai da rikici, wanda ke fama da rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson tana da kyau a wannan rawar da ke tunatar da halin Theresa May, amma labarin bai ba da abubuwa da yawa don manyan jirage ba.
