Kuma wannan wani ne Johnny English, wanda ba shi da kwarewa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata makarantar sakandare, amma yana koyar da darussan da ba na hukuma ba game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: akwai wasu lambobi masu ban sha'awa a nan, saboda English yana ba mu makarantar leƙen asiri kamar fim ɗin "Rock School".
