Mene ne bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke nuna jerin taurari masu ban mamaki waɗanda za su yi aiki a kan manufa mai ban mamaki: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival zai karbi dubban mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba wai kawai don kallon wasan kwaikwayo kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
Bikin Baƙi na Duniya, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, ƙungiyar masu ba da shawara da ke fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar ƙara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar magance ta.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan suna son biyan tikiti na VIP) masu kallo dole ne su yi aiki da yawa, ko "ayyuka", kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu mahimmanci waɗanda ke taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen a cikin shekaru 12 da suka gabata wajen cimma burinta?
Shin kyautar kyauta ga mutane da ke ba da kyauta kyauta hanya ce ta gaske don lallashe su su nemi aiki, ko kuma wannan wani lamari ne na "clicktivism" - tunanin cewa akwai bambanci tsakanin sanya hannu kan takardar neman izini ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet?
Global Citizen ya ce tun daga shekara ta 2011, ya samu "aiki" fiye da miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa da suka matsa wa juna don cimma wasu manufofi.
Wannan ya sa shugabannin duniya suka sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambata alkawura 390 da sanarwar da ta samo asali daga ayyukanta, tare da aƙalla dala biliyan 10 da aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a faɗin duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta a Burtaniya wacce ke hada masu saka jari da masu aiwatar da manufofi da suka himmatu wajen "taimakon yara su cimma burinsu", wanda ya yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen karancin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da na Global Citizens kamar mu duka, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin bayanin kula na tarihin", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, ga taron jama'a a wani wasan kwaikwayo na rayuwa a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kara da cewa, bayan an matsa wa Birtaniya sama da dubu biyar domin inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta samar da kudade don wani shiri mai suna Power of Nutrition, wanda zai shafi mata da yara miliyan biyar, tare da bada tallafi kan abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafin, "Me ya sa ka yi tunanin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa: "Wannan hanya ce mai tsawo da kuma wahala - a wasu lokatai muna faɗuwa kuma muna kasawa.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin ɗan ƙasa da na anti-apartheid da suka gabace mu, domin mun fi ƙarfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe suna cikin masu zane-zane da za su yi a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman suka gabatar.
