"Idan ya cancanta", Washington na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta don hana makamashin Rasha isa kasuwanni, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, a cewar Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi zargin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, musamman inda ta zo da gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine don su nemi samar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, a cikin kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga mai mulki, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a hana shi.
"Amurka tana da karfin da ke cikin sojan ruwanta na tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa a bude suke, kuma idan ya cancanta, ta sanya shingayen da za su hana makamashi zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke yana jawabi ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da dangantakar da ke tsakaninta da Rasha da Iran, inda ya ce su ma iri daya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha shine, kusan, don haɓaka da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha a matsayin "mai sihiri mai sihiri" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan magana ta zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don wannan, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, gami da shugaban kansa, suna ƙoƙarin lallashe Jamus ta watsar da "mara kyau" aikin bututun Nord Stream, wanda a cewar Trump ya mai da Berlin "ɗan kurkuku" na Moscow.
Moscow ta sha bayyana cewa bututun mai mai mai da dala biliyan 11 da ake kira Nord Stream, wanda zai ninka yawan ƙarfinsa zuwa wajen biliyan 110 na murabba'in mita, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce Washington ta yi adawa da wannan shiri ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma wannan misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba kuma masu amfani da makamashi su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya haifar da mummunar amsa daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da aikinsa.
Babban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta nisanta kanta da manufofin EU kan makamashi da kuma yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu da ke tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, babban jami'in hukumar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta "bincika sosai" ko za ta nemi shugabancin kasar a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "bincika sosai" ko za ta nemi takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben fidda gwani.
A lokacin wani taron tattaunawa na jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da yiwuwar yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a matsayin babban mai kula", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi nazari sosai game da yiwuwar yin takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin muhawarar da aka yi a cikin taron, yana mai cewa "yana jagorantar kasar a hanyar da ba daidai ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da kuma wanda ya zaba a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani sakon Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "a fili muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zaben".
Sai dai kuma, wani binciken da aka gudanar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu zaben Warren ba su yarda da cewa ya kamata ta nemi shugaban kasa a 2020.
Kashi 59 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata 'yar majalisar dattijai ta yi takara ba, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta yi.
Kashi 32 cikin dari sun goyi bayan takararsa.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya mafi girma ga takarar tsohon gwamna Gwamna Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38 cikin dari a cikin goyon bayan takarar da ake iya yi da kashi 48 cikin dari.
Sauran fitattun sunayen Jam'iyyar Democrat da aka tattauna game da yiwuwar takara a 2020 sun haɗa da tsohon Mataimakin Shugaban ƙasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance a watan Janairu, a cewar Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta ambaci damuwa ta PTSD na Track Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan da ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
A ranar Litinin da yamma, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani mummunan aiki a cikin gida.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da yake fuskanta bayan ya dawo, zan iya fahimtar wasu iyalai da ke fama da ciwon bayan-ciwon kai da wasu raunukan da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta a wani taron goyon bayan Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira wannan kama "giwa a cikin dakin" kuma ta ce ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "suna dawowa da ɗan bambanci, sun dawo da wuya, suna tambayar kansu ko akwai wannan girmamawa ga abin da 'yan uwansa sojoji da' yan saman jirgi, da duk sauran membobin soja, suka ba ƙasar".
An kama Track Palin a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mace da kuma mallakar makami a cikin giya, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun ofishin 'yan sanda na Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalan da aka yi game da sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun bada goyon bayansu wajen kalubalantar sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana masu fama da rikicin gida da na kungiyoyi mafaka.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun aika da wata sanarwa ta amicus curiae (abokan kotu) a ranar Juma'a a Washington, DC, don tallafawa wani mai neman mafaka wanda ke kalubalantar wannan manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a cikin shari'ar Grace da Sessions da Civil Liberties Union ta gabatar a watan Agusta ba game da manufar.
Mutumin ya ce abokin aikinsa "da 'ya'yansa, 'yan kungiya masu ta'addanci" sun yi masa fyaɗe, amma hukumomin Amurka sun ƙi karɓar shi a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An kama mai gabatar da kara a Texas.
Hukumomin gwamnati da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da yawan masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsalolin gangs da tashin hankali na gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke shawarar da Hukumar Kula da Harkokin Shige da Fice ta yanke a 2014 da ta ba da damar baƙi marasa izini da suka tsere daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a wata sanarwa a ranar Jumma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihohi, tarayya da kuma dokokin duniya".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a bincika dukan aikace-aikacen neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayin da ke tattare da su; wannan haramcin ya saɓa wa wannan ƙa'idar", in ji sanarwar amicus curiae.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi jayayya a cikin wannan sanarwa cewa hana 'yan sanda shiga baƙi yana shafar tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa baƙi sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma "samu ma'aikata da ake buƙata".
Babban lauyan Amurka Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga tashin hankali da kuma ƙungiyoyin 'yan daba a watan Yuni.
"Suna da damar samun mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron su bisa kabilanci, addini, kasa ko kasancewarsu a wata kungiya ta musamman ko kuma ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga watan Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a ko'ina a duniya ba.
An yi ta kokarin ceto mutane a Palu yayin da adadin wadanda suka mutu ya ninka a wani lokaci na neman wadanda suka tsira
Amma, waɗanda suka tsira daga wannan bala'in sun ƙara baƙin ciki.
"Yau yanayi ya yi muni sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mata 'yar shekara 35, mahaifiyar wani jariri namiji da ke fama da zazzaɓi, yayin da take ƙarfafa shi a wani wurin da ake ceto mutane a birnin Palu da aka halaka.
"Kowane minti, motar asibiti tana kawo ƙarin gawawwaki.
Akwai karancin ruwa mai tsafta".
An ga mazauna garin suna komawa gidajen da aka rushe don su ceci duk abin da za su iya samu a cikin kayansu da ke cikin ruwa.
An ji wa daruruwan mutane rauni kuma asibitoci da girgizar ƙasar mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta lalata sun cika.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, kamar Dwi Haris, wanda ya karye haƙarƙarinsa da kafada, suna kwance a waje da Asibitin Sojojin Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda mummunan alamun da ke ci gaba.
Idanunsa suna cike da hawaye sa'ad da yake ba da labarin yadda ya ji sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa ta girgiza shi a ɗakin otal ɗin bene na biyar da yake tare da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Ba mu da lokacin ceton kanmu.
Na makale a cikin bangon bango, ina tsammanin", in ji Haris ga Associated Press, yana mai cewa danginsa suna cikin gari don bikin aure.
"Na ji matata tana kuka don taimako, amma sai babu magana.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita da ɗiyata ba.
Ina fatan suna cikin koshin lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "tsoratar da mutane" da "tallace-tallacen farfaganda"
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da karin kudin da aka biya na jaridar China Daily a jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben majalisar wakilai na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin Trump na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna farkon abin da jami'an Amurka, a cikin jawabai ga Reuters, suka kira sabon mataki a cikin yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallata tallace-tallace don bunkasa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai tsanani wanda ya ga bangarorin biyu suna saka haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa daga bangaren juna.
Kudaden harajin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara su ne don shafar masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohin da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, "yana shiga cikin wannan barazanar ta hanyar buga tallan talla a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"Ta hanyar yada wannan farfaganda, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin magana da' yan jarida ta hanyar buga wani tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a cikin bankuna a nan Beijing, mun sami muryoyin 'yan adawa kaɗan kuma ba za mu taɓa ganin ainihin bambancin ra'ayi da Sinawa za su iya yi game da mummunan yanayin tattalin arzikin ƙasarsu ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin tsananin ikon jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta China", in ji shi.
Ya kuma ce "wani babban jaridar kasar Sin ya ki buga" labarinsa, ko da yake bai bayyana ko wane ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da mata kafin zaben fidda gwani da Kavanaugh ya yi, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin
A daidai lokacin da manyan 'yan Republican da dama ke goyon bayan kuma kare wanda aka zaba a kotun kolin kasar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa hakan na iya janyo mummunan martani, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben da ke tafe.
An samu tashin hankali a kan wannan lamari kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun bayyana a fili cewa suna son su yi zabe.
Waɗannan abubuwa ba su da wata hanya ta komawa baya", Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell da ke Jami'ar Syracuse ya gaya wa The Hill.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa matsa lamba na karshe daga Sanata Jeff Flake (Jamhuriyar Republican daga Arizona) don gudanar da binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kungiyar MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C. ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun rera waka "Nuwamba tana kan kofa!" lokacin da suka yi zanga-zanga a harabar majalisar dattijai, saboda 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a sun zabi ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya ruwaito.
"Jami'an Democrat za su yi farin ciki da kuma motsawa sosai", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai bincike a siyasa.
"Mutane suna cewa ta tsufa; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu zaɓe a yankunan da ke kusa da birane da kuma matasa masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, ba sa yawan yin zabe".
Tun kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana zargin cin zarafinsa kan wanda aka nada zuwa Kotun Koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya samun mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan ya zama abin takaici ga Jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai hau kan kujerar alkali, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da batun da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa 'yan Democrat su yi zabe, ga tashar labarai.
Amma jama'ar Amurka sun rabu a kan wanda za su amince da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da karamin rinjaye da ke tare da na farko.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun gaskata da shaidar Ford ko kuma sun gaskata da shi, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh ko kuma sun gaskata da shi.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imani cewa Kavanaugh yana iya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a shaidar da ya bayar, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka faɗi haka game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya gabatar da shawarar, FBI ta fara bincike kan zargin Ford da kuma na wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, a cewar Guardian.
Ford ta shaidawa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi lalata da ita a lokacin da take shan giya, lokacin da take 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa wanda aka zaba a kotun kolin ya nuna al'aurarsa a lokacin da suka halarci wani biki a lokacin da suke Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai amfani da intanet ya yi niyyar samar da sabuwar intanet da za ta yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kirkiro wani kamfanin da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikinsa na baya bayan nan, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da ke amfani da tsarin bude tushen Berners-Lee, Solid.
Wannan yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawarar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda ke da damar samun bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wasa da cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "kayan ajiyar bayanan kan layi", ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ɗauke da jerin sunayen abokanka, jerin abubuwan da za ka yi, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na kanka da kuma na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa ajiyar bayanai ta kan layi ta musamman ita ce, mai amfani ne kaɗai zai iya yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shine samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa sa Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shiryen cikin gida da aka ɗauka don aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu kirkirar fasaha a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su kawo sauyi gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya koma baya cikin dare.
"Ba mu tambayar su izini".
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizon da aka kirkira tare da Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da yake yana ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama wanda ya kafa kuma darektan Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: girmamawa ga limamin da aka ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria a yakin duniya na farko
Limamin cocin Ingila daya tilo da ya samu Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na daya a matsayin mai yaki an girmama shi a garinsu shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
Laftanar Lt. Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 tare da kai hari kan Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma sai wani ɗan harbi ya kashe shi kwanaki huɗu bayan haka kuma bai san cewa an ba shi babbar lambar yabo ta soja ba.
Jikanta biyu sun bude wani allon tunawa a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikinsu, Michael Vann, ya ce "abin da ke da alama ne" cewa an gabatar da wannan alama daidai shekaru 100 bayan da aka ba da lambar yabo ga kakansa.
A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa ta tsallaka Ruwa na Saint-Quentin "a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai ƙarfi daga bindigogi da na'urori masu linzami".
Sai ya ruga zuwa layin wuta kuma, "da ƙarfin zuciya", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya kai hari kan bindiga da kansa kuma ya kashe sojoji uku na rukunin.
An kashe Lt. Col. Vann ne daga hannun wani dan bindiga a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "wani abu ne da na sani ba zan taɓa iya yin daidai da shi ba, amma kuma darasi ne na tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun ajiye wani furanni bayan bikin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce ya "ji daɗin halartar bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "ƙarfin hali na ainihin gwarzo yana nunawa ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
Masu sha'awar wasan kungiya masu tsaka-tsakin da suka farka duk dare don kallon Bellator 206 sun kalli Peppa Pig a maimakon haka
