Tom Daley ya ji "ƙanƙanta" game da jima'i
Mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin ya fi kowa saboda jima'i amma hakan ya sa ya zama mai nasara.
Mai wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci hakan ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A wata hira da aka yi da ita a Radio 4 na farko Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ta bayyana cewa ta yi magana game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce zama uba ya sa ya daina damuwa da samun lambar yabo a gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin na dogon lokaci Kirsty Young ta ɗauki hutu na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin mai banƙyama a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙananan" ga kowa saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba a cikin zamantakewa don son yara maza da 'yan mata".
A kalmominsa, "har wa yau, wannan tunanin cewa mun fi wasu girma da kuma bambanci shi ne ainihin dalilin da ya sa na sami iko da ƙarfin yin nasara".
Manufarsa ita ce ya nuna cewa shi "wani ne", in ji shi, don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai sa'ad da ya gano cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Wannan gwarzon zinare na Olympics sau biyu ya zama fitaccen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da halartar wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe don dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya bayyana cewa yana farin ciki cewa zai iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Gwarzon gwarzon ya ce, "Na yi mamaki sosai sa'ad da na soma soyayya da wani mutum, wato, Dustin Lance Black, wani ɗan Amirka da ya yi fim a shekara ta 2013.
Daley ta yi aure a shekarar da ta gabata da wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, duk da cewa ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da muka sha wahala sosai a lokacin da muke ƙanana" - ya fara halartar gasar Olympics yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon kansa shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce, yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya wanda ya sha wahala da yawa.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni na bara, mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "duk hangen nesan sa" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne samun zinare", in ji ta.
"Amma ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
"Robbie ne zinariyar da na samu a gasar Olympics".
Ɗansa yana da sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambayi shi shi ne ko suna da tikiti na wasannin London na 2012 domin yana so ya kasance a gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa cewa ba za ka kasance a nan don ka zauna a jere na farko ba, Baba", in ji ta.
"Ina riƙe da hannunsa ne kawai lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji ta.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya sami lambar tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine abin da na yi mafarkin rayuwata: yin iyo a gaban 'yan uwanmu a gasar Olympics ... babu abin da ya fi wannan jin dadi", in ji shi.
Wannan ya kuma sa ya zaɓi waƙar da ya fara rerawa, wato Proud, ta Heather Small, wadda ta sa shi farin ciki sa'ad da yake shirin halartar gasar Olympics.
Desert Island Discs yana watsa shirye-shiryen BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na yamma.
Mickelson saukar da siffar a kan benci a Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasa na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup ranar Asabar, amma zai bukaci ya dawo cikin siffar da ya dace don hana wannan ci gaba daga nuna rashin sa'a.
Mickelson, yana buga gasar shekara biyu a karo na 12, wanda ya kasance mafi yawan halarta, ya kasance a cikin kujera ta hanyar kyaftin Jim Furyk a wasanni hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya kasance a yawancin lokaci a cikin ƙungiyoyin Amurka, mai nasara sau biyar a gasar zakarun maza ya raba rana tsakanin aikin goyon baya da aiki a wasan da yake yi a filin wasa, yana fatan gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Da yake bai taɓa buga kwallo mai kaifi ba ko da a lokacin da ya fi ƙwarewa, ɗan wasan mai shekara 48 ba shi da kyau a filin wasan Le Golf National, inda dogon tsalle-tsalle yakan hukunta masu yin kuskure.
Kuma idan filin wasa bai isa ba, Mickelson a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi zai fafata da zakaran gasar Open ta Burtaniya Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da mai farawa Tommy Fleetwood, inda ya lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da ke da ci hudu a raga a wasan farko na wasanni 12 na wasan kwaikwayo, sun fara da kyau, Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa yana da tabbaci a kan mutanensa, amma bai ce zai iya yin hakan ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci aikin da nake da shi a yau sosai, sai ya bugi baya na, ya rungume ni kuma ya ce zan yi aikin gobe".
"Ya ke da yawa amincewa da kansa.
Shi zakara ne da ake girmamawa wanda ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga waɗannan ƙungiyoyi a baya, kuma wannan makon ma.
Wataƙila ban taɓa ganin shi yana wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunani game da ƙarin, amma wannan shine yadda ya faru kuma wannan shine yadda muka yi tunanin cewa ya kamata mu ci gaba.
Yana son ya shiga cikin wasan kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a gasar Ryder Cup.
Hakan na iya nuna ƙarshen aikinsa na gasar Ryder wanda bai taɓa yin nasara kamar yadda ya yi a wasan kansa ba.
Mickelson ya ci 18, ya yi rashin nasara 20, kuma ya ci bakwai, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya haifar da wasu abubuwan da ba a iya fahimta ba ga tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ban dariya da kuma ban dariya, yana son yin wasa da mutane kuma yana da kyau a cikin ɗakin ɗakin", in ji ta.
"Ina tsammanin 'yan wasan matasa sun ji daɗin yin wasa da shi a wannan makon, wanda ya kasance abin ban sha'awa.
Yana ba da fiye da wasa kawai".
Kyaftin din Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa babban damarsa na iya ɓacewa cikin ɗan lokaci
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai ya san cewa shugabancinsa da aka yi a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup zai iya zama abin takaici.
Dan Danish din ya fara wasa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama inda wata kungiya da Seve Ballesteros ta jagoranci ta ci gaba da samun maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma ta tsallaka layin ƙarshe tare da hanci tare da mafi ƙanƙanta daga cikin gefuna, ta lashe 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"A koyaushe muna kokarin tuna cewa muna da fa'ida mai yawa a Valderrama; muna da fa'ida mai yawa a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma kusa", in ji Bjorn, a hoton, bayan ya kalli nasarar 2018 Turma da 5-3, duka a ranar Juma'a da jiya, don jagoranci 10-5 a Le Golf National.
Ta haka ne tarihi ya nuna mini da kuma duk wanda ke cikin wannan tawagar cewa wannan ba ta ƙare ba tukuna.
Ku yi iya ƙoƙarinku a gobe.
Ku tafi ku yi kome da kyau.
Wannan ba zai ƙare ba har sai mun sami maki a kan maki.
Muna da manufa guda, wato mu ci wannan kofin kuma a nan ne ya kamata mu mai da hankali.
A koyaushe ina cewa ina mai da hankali ne ga 'yan wasa 12 da ke gefenmu, amma mun san waɗanda ke gefenmu: 'yan wasa mafi kyau a duniya".
Bjorn ya yi farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a kan wani filin golf mai wuya, ya daɗa: "Ba zan taɓa yin nasara a kan kaina ba.
Za a fuskanci kalubale dabam gobe.
Abin da ke da muhimmanci a gobe shi ne yadda mutum zai yi aiki, kuma hakan ya ƙunshi wani aiki dabam.
Yana da kyau mu kasance tare da abokin tarayya sa'ad da abubuwa suke tafiya daidai, amma sa'ad da muke kanmu, ana gwada iyawarmu a matsayin 'yan wasan golf sosai.
Wannan shi ne saƙon da ya kamata a isar wa 'yan wasan: Ku yi iya ƙoƙarinku gobe.
Yanzu za su bar abokin aurensu kuma dole ne ya yi iya ƙoƙarinsa".
A bambanci da Bjorn, abokin hamayyarsa Jim Furyk zai nemi 'yan wasan su yi aiki mafi kyau a matsayin mutum fiye da yadda suke aiki tare, tare da ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a bangarorin biyu na wannan babban juyin juya halin a ranar ƙarshe, kasancewar yana cikin ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline kafin ta rasa lokacin da Turai ta cire "Miracle a Madinah" daga cikin akwatin.
"Na tuna da kowace kalma", in ji shi a amsa tambayar game da yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin a 1999, ya motsa 'yan wasansa zuwa rana ta ƙarshe.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna so ku samu wannan saurin farawa kamar abin da kuka gani a Brookline da abin da kuka gani a Madina.
Sa'ad da wannan ƙarfin ya koma gefe ɗaya, matsin lamba yana da yawa a waɗannan ɓangarorin da ke tsakanin.
Mun tsara 'yan wasanmu daidai da yadda muke ji, kuma za mu yi sihiri gobe".
Thomas, tare da aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar kai hari, ya fuskanci Rory McIlroy a cikin babban wasan, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter sauran Turawa a farkon rabin tsari.
"Na zaɓi wannan rukunin 'yan wasa ta wannan tsari saboda na yi imanin cewa ya rufe duka hanyar", in ji Bjorn game da zaɓin da ya yi don singles.
An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An shirya sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus da zai shiga aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma zai bukaci a jira a kalla har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ke fuskantar lalacewa da kuma tsadar da ke karuwa, a cewar kafofin yada labarai na gida.
An jinkirta shigar da "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton kakakin soja.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan bayarwa sun lalata makomar wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar sojin ta ba da umarni a 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An san cewa za su kasance da babbar makami mai linzami, da kuma wasu makamai masu linzami da na jirgin ruwa, da kuma wasu fasahohin da ba a sani ba kamar rage radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran muhimman halaye sun hada da tsawon lokaci tsakanin kulawa, wanda zai ba da damar tura sabbin jiragen ruwa zuwa ayyukan da zasu iya wuce shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, saboda jinkirin da ake yi, jiragen yaƙi na zamani da ake gani a matsayin hanyar da Jamus za ta nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje, za su zama tsofaffi sa'ad da suka soma aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
An samu labarin jirgin ruwan F125 a bara lokacin da rundunar sojin Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da sojojin suka mayar da jirgi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa bayan an ba da shi.
Ba a san komai game da dalilan da suka sa aka mayar da su ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu "kasawa na kayan aiki da software" waɗanda za su sa jirgin yaƙi ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi a cikin aikin yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, tun da jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120, kawai rabin adadin da ake bukata a cikin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma san cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon sojojin don shigar da ƙarin ayyuka a nan gaba.
An yi imani cewa "Rheinland-Pfalz" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jiragen ruwa iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da gazawar kayan aiki, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya, har da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, yana zama matsala.
An ce wannan ya kai dala biliyan 3.1 mai ban mamaki, wanda ya karu daga dala biliyan 2.2 da aka tsara.
Matsalolin da ke addabar sababbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu muhimmanci musamman a cikin hasken da aka ba da kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus ya yarda cewa a yanzu haka sojojin ruwa ba su da jiragen ruwa da za su iya amfani da su".
Ya ce matsalar ta karu sosai a tsawon lokaci, saboda an daina amfani da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa ba tare da samun wasu da za su maye gurbinsu ba.
A ƙarshe, ya yi nadamar cewa babu ɗayan frigates na Baden-Wuerttemberg da za su iya shiga cikin sojojin ruwa.
