Girgizar ƙasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a ta kashe, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da aka katse sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani game da yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke gefen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, wanda ke da matsayi na ƙananan hukumomi fiye da lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki a lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi daga cikinsu a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, manyan girgizar ƙasa sun afka wa yammacin tsibirin Sumatra.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa da ba ta da zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haddasa halaka da firgici tsakanin mutanen da ke tuna da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekara ta 2004.
A wannan lokacin babu wata tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin kango.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a tsibirin yawon buɗe ido na Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine-gine, ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a ware na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an tsare shi kan zargin cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, mazaunin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki a binciken cin zarafin gida da kuma tsayayya da kama, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda na Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, sa'ad da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai ƙarar laifuffukan da ake zargi, sai ya ƙwace wayar ta.
Palin tana tsare a cibiyar tsare mutane a Mat-Su, a kan belin dala 500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban alƙali a ranar Asabar, yana mai cewa "ba shi da laifi", in ji tashar.
Palin tana fuskantar tuhuma kan wasu laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za a iya yanke mata hukuncin daurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake iya yankewa da ɗaurin kwana ɗaya da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka gabatar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017 an zarge shi da cin zarafin mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyar Sarah Palin ta kira 'yan sanda don kai rahoton zargin da ake yi mata.
Ana sauraron shari'ar a kotun tsoffin sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali a gida, da tsoma baki wajen kai rahoton aikata laifukan tashin hankali a gida, da kuma mallakar bindiga a cikin shan giya, dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarka ta zarge ka da dūkan fuskarka.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka a shekarar 2016 daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji bayan da ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da tashin hankali na bayan-tashin hankali wanda ya samo asali daga aikinsa a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
An katse wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku ne a yankin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Ana yada bidiyo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin da ya faru.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya afku a bakin tekun.
Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta bukaci hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York.
Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta New York ta nemi hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da wata mota da aka yi hayar ta a Home Depot don kai hari a watan Oktoba a kan hanyar keke a West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da keke.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni da gangan, a cewar sanarwar da aka yi a kudancin New York.
An ce duka laifuffukan biyu za su iya jawo hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta yanke hukunci a kan laifuffuka 22 da Saipov ya aikata, ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin aikin aikata laifuka, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsari mai kyau da kuma tunanin da aka yi", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya kashe shi a matsayin "m, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da New York ta Kudu ba ta nemi hukuncin kisa ba.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an sauya hukuncin zuwa rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe wani mutum a New York da ya yi kisa a kotu. An kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union shekaru biyu kafin lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenbergs a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna wani nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi don kai harin bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi izinin rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin Saipov ya ce sun "mamaki" da hukuncin da ake yi.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin da ake yi na ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da samun 'yanci ba, zai ƙara tsawaita cutar da ke tattare da waɗannan abubuwan ga duk wanda ke ciki", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce ya kamata Nigel Farage ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "daukar sojojin jama'a" a yau a wani zanga-zanga a majalisun Conservatives.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar UKIP ya ce 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" daga 'yan adawa da Turai, yayin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya nuna cewa ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya ce a taron Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta riga ta fita" idan Farage ya zama Ministan Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta na sulhunta 'yan uwanta masu rarrabuwar kawuna ya kasance sananne ga masu ra'ayin mazan jiya da ke goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a cikin EU, wadanda suka shirya wani zanga-zangar Brexit daban a birnin.
Firaministan ta yi ta gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da shirin sulhunta, wanda aka fi sani da Shirin Chequers, a yayin da magoya bayan Brexit, masu ci gaba da zama a EU ke kai hare-hare.
Allies sun nace cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da zanga-zangar, tilasta masu shakkar Euro da Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin ta da "hargitsi".
Mr Bone ya ce a taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son "kawar da shirin".
Bone ya ce ya kamata a baiwa Farage wasu hakkoki a tattaunawar da aka yi da Brussels.
"Idan shi ne ke da alhakin, da mun riga mun fita", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan ci gaba da kare Brexit amma ya kamata mu kawo karshen shirin".
Da yake ƙarfafa adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a Yaƙe-yaƙe na Duniya biyu don mu zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokin ƙasarmu".
Bone ya musanta zargin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben raba gardama na 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son zama ba daidai bane".
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ma ta halarci zanga-zangar, inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa kawai: Madam Firaminista, ku saurari jama'a.
Shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau a gaban jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da shi ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan gwagwarmayar da ke gudanar da yakin neman zabe a kan tituna da kuma wanda muke bin zaɓe.
Ka bar shirin Chequers ka fara sauraro".
A wata wasikarsa ga Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Firai ministocin da suka iya cika alkawurran su ne kawai ke rike da ayyukansu".
Farage ya ce a wajen taron 'yan siyasa dole ne su "ji matsin lamba" idan sun shirya cin amanar zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan ya zama batun amincewa tsakanin mu - jama'a - da kuma siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za su samu damar yin hakan ba".
Da yake jawabi ga taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku matsa wa 'yan siyasarmu lamba, wadanda ke kan iyakar cin amanar Brexit.
Muna so mu garzaya da sojojin kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai alfahari da mulkin kanta".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a Birmingham sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Jama'a masu fafutuka sun yi amfani da banners da ke cewa "Tari'a ta Conservative ta yi watsi da Brexit" bayan an kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Wakilin Labour a majalisar dattawa, Andrew Adonis, ya soki 'yan Conservative saboda matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta tare da aikace-aikacen jam'iyyar a buɗe taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su shirya tsarin kwamfuta da duk fasahar don 'Canada mafi yawa,' don iyakar da ba ta da alaƙa, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba", in ji shi.
Wannan ba gaskiya ba ne.
Babu wani abu mai kyau kamar Brexit", in ji shi.
Warren na shirin "tunanin da gaske" game da yiwuwar neman shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa, 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat daga Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomar ta a lokacin wata muhawara a jihar a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, tana neman sake zaɓe a watan Nuwamba da wakilin Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Trump a shekarar 2016 a Massachusetts.
An yi hasashen cewa zai iya fuskantar Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a yammacin Asabar a Holyoke shi ne na 36 da ya gana da masu jefa kuri'a a matsayin muhawara tun lokacin da aka naɗa Trump.
Wani ɗan'uwa ya tambaye shi ko yana son ya yi takarar shugaban ƙasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mata za su je Washington su gyara matsalolin gwamnatinmu kuma hakan ya hada da mace a matsayi na farko".
An kama shi a game da kisan Wayde Sims na kungiyar LSU Tigers
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa sun kama wani da ake zargi da kisan gillar da aka yi wa dan wasan kwando na LSU Tigers, Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge sun sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a wani taron manema labarai da suka yi da misalin karfe 11 na safiyar yau.
'Yan sanda sun fitar da wani bidiyo na harbi a ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da aka gani a hotunan.
An kashe Sims, dan shekara 20, a kusa da jami'ar Southern a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya ji rauni a kansa, daga bisani ya mutu", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga manema labarai a ranar Asabar, a cewar 247sports.
Wayde yana kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
Simpson ya amsa tambayoyin da aka yi masa kuma ya yarda da kasancewarsa a wurin, yana riƙe da bindiga, ya yarda da harbi Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da ya yi tsayayya ba kuma an kai shi ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge na Gabas.
Sims, dan wasa mai tsayi 1,98 a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 kuma ya fara wasa sau 10 a kakar wasa ta bara, yana da kimanin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da 2.9 a kowace wasa.
Gasar Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusanci taken duniya tare da nasara akan Sebastian Vettel a bayan umarnin tawagar
Ya bayyana a lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi nasara a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa umarnin ƙungiyar a Mercedes za su taka muhimmiyar rawa a tseren.
Daga kan hanya, Bottas ya fara da kyau kuma ya bar Hamilton a baya yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a cikin murabba'i biyu na farko, yana ba Vettel damar kai wa abokin aikinsa hari.
Vettel ya fara shiga cikin akwatin, kuma hakan ya sa Hamilton ya fuskanci cunkoson ababen hawa a ƙarshen rukuni, wanda zai iya zama mai yanke hukunci.
Mercedes ta shiga cikin akwatin jirgi da baya kuma ta bi bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya wuce shi bayan gwagwarmaya mai tsanani, bayan haka direban Ferrari ya bar cikin filin wasa ba tare da son rai ba, yana fuskantar haɗarin yanke hukunci bayan gyara hanya biyu don kare kansa a kwana na uku.
Max Verstappen ya tashi daga layin ƙarshe kuma yana matsayi na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Ya jagoranci mafi yawan tseren, yana canza tayoyin da wuri, wanda zai ba shi damar yin sauri a ƙarshen, yana neman wuce Kimi Raikkonen don kammala a matsayi na huɗu.
Ya zo cikin raga a zagaye na 44 amma bai sami damar inganta saurin sa ba a zagaye takwas da suka gabata, wanda ya ba Raikkonen damar zama na huɗu.
"Yau rana ce mai wuya domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai kyau a duk tsawon karshen mako kuma ya kasance mai kirki, ya bar ni in wuce shi.
"Mutumin ya yi aiki mai kyau, wanda ya ba mu damar kammala a matsayi biyu na farko", in ji Hamilton.
Yadda Sukan Yi Magana da Jiki
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein ba'a a wani taron jama'a a ranar Asabar saboda dagewarta cewa ba za ta bayyana wasikar Christine Blasey Ford da ke zargin Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada zuwa Kotun Koli ba, da cin zarafin jima'i.
Da yake jawabi a wani taron jama'a a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar Ford a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai ba, maimakon haka ya ce abin da ke faruwa a majalisar dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne, masu ƙeta da kuma ƙarya".
"Ku dubi abin ban mamaki da ke faruwa a majalisar dattijai a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan, ku dubi fushin, ku dubi yadda mutane suke da mugunta da mugunta da kuma ƙarya", in ji Trump.
"Lokacin da muka ga bayanan da aka fallasa da kuma sanarwar da aka fitar, kuma suka ce, 'Oh, ba ni ba ne.
Ba ni ba ne na yi hakan.
Ka tuna da wannan?
Dianne Feinstein, shin ka soma wannan matsalar ne da kanka?
Ka tuna da amsar da ta bayar, ta fitar da takardar?
A'a, ba haka ba ne.
Ba na guduwa.'
To, ku dakata.
"Mun tsere daga gare mu ... a'a, ba mu bane", in ji ta, tana kwaikwayon sanatan.
Feinstein ya karbi wasikar da ke dauke da cikakken bayanin zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh wanda Ford ya aika a watan Yuli kuma ya tsere a farkon watan Satumba, amma ya musanta cewa tseren ya fito ne daga ofishinsa.
"Ban rufe maganganun Dr. Ford ba, ban bayyana labarinta ba", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin, a cewar The Hill.
"Ta roƙe ni in ba ta labarin, kuma na girmama ta".
Amma ƙaryatakarsa ba ta gamsar da shugaban ba, wanda ya yi sharhi a taron ranar Asabar da dare: "Kun san, wannan mummunan magana ne.
Wataƙila ba ita ba ce, amma wannan ita ce mafi munin yaren da na taɓa gani".
