Yadda yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing
Farkon tashin hankalin da aka yi a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi muni sosai, kuma ko da yake ba a ga ƙarshen rikici a gani ba, daga ra'ayin masana, nisantar kasashen biyu na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara faɗakarwa a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su daga China da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminium.
Wannan makon ya kasance wurin da lamarin ya kara muni sosai da sabbin harajin da ke shafar kayayyaki masu darajar dala biliyan 200 (fam biliyan 150) da gaske ke biyan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da China ke shigowa Amurka.
Beijing ta yi martani a kan wannan batun, kwanan nan ta ɗaga haraji daga kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin bin sahun Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya yi kasa a gwiwa ba.
Komawa da Washington zai nuna cewa ta yi biyayya ga bukatun, amma nuna biyayya ga Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da karfinta, matsin lamba da yaƙin cinikayya da Amurka ya jawo zai iya taimaka wa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikinta.
"A gaskiya, cewa wani yanke shawara na siyasa daga Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da matsalar tattalin arziki a ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura da su za su iya tsammani", in ji Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke nazarin Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabuwar Tsaro ta Amirka.
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar ya ce kasar Syria a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka dawo
Syria ta ce a shirye take da dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ya shafe shekaru bakwai ana yaki.
A jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
Ya ce, "Yanzu haka, yanayin da ake ciki ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amura na yau da kullun.
Yanzu akwai dukkan yanayi don 'yan gudun hijirar su koma ƙasarsu da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye da suka shafi rayuwarsu da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suka rage a kasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi farin cikin samun taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da kasashen da ke goyon bayan tawaye za su ba shi ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a birnin Paris
Ƙasar Turai ta doke Amurka kuma ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 tare da ƙimar ƙarshe na 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta sha kaye shida a jere a Turai tun lokacin da ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai a 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar bayan da tawagar Denmark mai jagorancin Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ta bukaci domin doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya nuna yana da matukar wahala a kusan dukkanin gasar, ya jefa wasan farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 16, par 3, ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Gwanin golf na Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a duk zagayensa, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasan 4 da suka samu 5-0-0 tun lokacin da tsarin gasar ta yanzu ya fara a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi 5 da 4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kasa da duka a gasar zakarun Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce kwallo a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila a wasan da zai iya zama na karshe a gasar Ryder.
Wani tsoho na gasar Ryder Cup guda takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama dan Turai mafi yawan kyauta a duk gasar tare da 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
