Labaran Red Tide: Yawan ruwa ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cewar sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida, an samu raguwar yawan ruwan Red Tide a wasu yankunan Tampa Bay.
FWC ta sanar da cewa an gano yanayin da ya rage yawan tabo a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Red Tide ta shimfida kimanin kilomita 201 a gefen tekun, daga Pinellas County a arewa zuwa Lee County a kudu.
Ana iya samun tabo a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a yankuna kaɗan fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga Red Tide a gundumar Pasco.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan wurare a bakin teku ko a gabar jihar Pinella, ƙananan wurare a gabar jihar Hillsborough, ƙananan wurare a cikin jihar Manatee, ƙananan wurare a cikin jihar Sarasota, ƙananan wurare a Charlotte, ƙananan wurare a cikin jihar Lee, da ƙananan wurare a cikin jihar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotannin ciwon numfashi a kananan hukumomin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani rahoton ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
